				<h3 id="blog-name"><a href="http://snaggingbaseballs.mlblogs.com/">The Baseball Collector</a></h3>
				<h4 id="blog-desc">Zack Hample has snagged 4,662 balls from 48 different Major League stadiums. Find out how and see what else he's been up to...</h4>
